snippet.title: Johnny Depp & Signs of Domestic Abuse
snippet.description:
Hello Beautiful People! 

In this video I discuss Domestic Abuse in the relationship between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. With some clips and voice recordings we can see the truth behind their abusive relationship. I also go through some of the signs to look out for in an abusive relationship.

I give telephone and online counselling, if you are interested email 
mimztherapy@gmail.com

Mens Advice Line
0808 8010327
https://mensadviceline.org.uk/

Womens Aid
0808 2000 247
https://www.womensaid.org.uk/information-support/

Samaritans (24/7 service) – 116 123

National LGBT Domestic Abuse Helpline
Helpline: 0800 999 5428

FCO Forced Marriage Unit
Helpline: 020 7008 0151 (or 0044 20 7008 0151 if you are overseas)

Refuge
Helpline: 0808 2000 247 (24 hours)

My channel  includes a variety of advice/therapy videos, vlogs, storytime's, challenges, and lifestyle tips, tricks and tutorials! 

If you would like to support me on my Patreon for exclusive live conversations, one on one chats about my videos and thoughts & discuss next video options.
Click the link below
https://www.patreon.com/mimzyvidz

Please like, subscribe and click the bell!!

Find me on
Twitter: mimzyv
Instagram/Snapchat/Facebook: mimzyvidz

Business enquiries/ personal help questions please email mimzyvidz@gmail.com

Big Kisses!!

Mimzy :)
